tafsir[4]{c,v,t}:
  16,16,"and waymarks; and by the stars they are guided."
  16,17,"Is He who creates as he who does not create? Will you not remember?"
  16,19,"And God knows what you keep secret and what you publish."
  16,23,"Without a doubt God knows what they keep secret and what they publish; He loves not those that wax proud."